<template>
    <v-card>
        <v-list-item two-line>
            <v-list-item-content>
                <v-list-item-title>Przypisania Fibu</v-list-item-title>
                <v-list-item-subtitle>Znajdź lub aktualizuj bieżące przypisanie Fibu </v-list-item-subtitle>
            </v-list-item-content>
        </v-list-item>

        <v-divider></v-divider>

        <v-container>
            <v-card>
            <v-tabs
            color="deep-purple accent-4"
            right
            >
                <v-tab>Szukaj/Przypisz</v-tab>
                <v-tab>Zestawienie</v-tab>
            </v-tabs>

            <v-row class="d-inline-flex mt-3 ml-2">
                <v-col cols="5">
                    <v-autocomplete
                        dense
                        prepend-icon="mdi-magnify"
                        :items="fibunr"
                        label="Nr FIBU">
                    </v-autocomplete>
                </v-col>
                <v-col cols="7">
                    <v-autocomplete
                        dense
                        prepend-icon="mdi-magnify"
                        :items="fibuname"
                        label="Nazwa klienta">
                    </v-autocomplete>
                </v-col>
            </v-row>

            <v-row>
                <v-col cols="6">
                    <CardFibu />
                </v-col> 
                <v-col cols="4" class="d-column-flex">
                    <v-select
                    :items="salesreps"
                    dense
                    label="Handlowiec"
                    ></v-select>
                    <v-select
                    :items="prod"
                    dense
                    label="Produkt"
                    ></v-select>
                    <v-btn
                        color="purple"
                        rounded
                        outlined
                        class="mx-auto pos"
                        >
                        Przypisz
                    </v-btn>
                </v-col> 
            </v-row>    
            <!-- <v-card-actions>
          <v-spacer></v-spacer>
          <v-btn
          color="red darken-3"
            class="font-weight-regular"
            rounded
            outlined
            small
            @click="dialog = false"
          >
            Anuluj
          </v-btn>
          <v-btn
          color="green"
            class="font-weight-regular"
            rounded
            outlined
            small
            @click="dialog = false"
          >
            Zapisz
          </v-btn>
        </v-card-actions> -->
        </v-card>
        </v-container>   
    </v-card>
</template>

<script>
import CardFibu from '../Cards/CardFibu.vue'

export default {
    data() {
        return {
            dialog: false,
            fibunr: ['D123456', 'D063476', 'D087879'],
            fibuname: ['STALKO', 'ELECTROLUX', 'DELAVAL'],
            salesreps: ['Adam Kramer', 'Paweł Olkowski', 'Anna Alibożek', 'Izabela Oleksiak'],
            prod: ['AFR', 'SFR', 'TRNG', 'TRIG', 'TRNF', 'TRID', 'CLC']
        }
    },
    components: {
        CardFibu
    }
}
</script>

<style>

</style>
